"Angola by incorporating the following features:"
msgstr ""
"Odoo Sign memastikan kepatuhan penuh terhadap Undang-Undang Tanda Tangan "
"Elektronik Angola dengan menggabungkan fitur-fitur berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/sign/angola.rst:58
msgid ""
"While Odoo Sign is broadly applicable, there are certain exceptions where "
"electronic signatures may not be suitable or legally recognized in Angola:"
msgstr ""
"Meskipun Odoo Sign dapat diterapkan secara luas, terdapat beberapa "
"pengecualian di mana tanda tangan elektronik mungkin tidak sesuai atau "
"diakui secara hukum di Angola:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/sign/angola.rst:69
msgid ""
