"stating :guilabel:`Some required fields are not valid`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/global_filters.rst:133
msgid ""
"Consider a *Relation* filter with the :guilabel:`Related model` set "
"as :guilabel:`Contact`. The :guilabel:`Field matching` *CRM* lead "
"(`crm.lead`) pivot data sources are set to :guilabel:`Customer`."
