"Templat Spreadsheet`. Hapus :guilabel:`Templat Saya` :ref:`filter <search/"
"preconfigured-filters>` untuk melihat semua templat dalam database."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/templates.rst:133
msgid ""
"To edit an existing template, click `✎ Edit` next to the desired template. "
